DATA "BREAK", "BSC","BREAK","breaks out of a switch statement or a loop

Synopsis

break

Description

break transfers control immediately outside the enclosing loop or switch statement. This is the preferred way of leaving such a statement.

Example
 
for a=1 to 10 
  break 
  print \"Hi\" 
next a 

